  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5705757/" class="title-link">中国共产党—收缩与调适：误判连连</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5705757"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2429292/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2429292-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2429292/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">优游卒岁</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-12-20"
      class="main-meta">2012-12-20 12:06:53</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5705757_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  买沈大伟教授这本书，我是犹豫再三。《中国共产党：收缩与调适》在我网上书店的收藏夹里，静静地躺了很长时间。沈大伟教授是早知其名，不过他的著作却一直未读过，很想了解其观点。但看其书名，写这样的题材，能够在国内出版，要么是其观点符合当权者的口味，要么就是惨遭阉割...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5705757/#comments">(9回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">35有用 / 7没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
